{"tid":2058342,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"有經驗租工廈做studio 既入","createTime":"2020-06-10T05:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T16:28:11.000Z","uid":8932,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"50973017ddf6224d41f621aaf3d9caee995b9a66","tid":2058342,"uid":8932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"因為政見同土地問題 所以 想租間工廈做studio 主要擺野 同 做野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實已經忍撚左成年 到近擺真係忍唔撚到 狂開火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔會過夜訓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想知 有咩野要注意 <br />\n我想要靚裝修 同 獨立厠所 加淋浴 <br />\n唔洗大 100以內就得 想知而家市價大約幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外 想知而家工廈既衛生情況 會唔會好多塵 同蛇蟲鼠蟻 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會唔會有經驗巴打 可以詳細分享下經驗 或者說服我唔好租工廈 草多2個錢 正正經經租間屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：男 窮撚 月入 22k 5k 家用 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">有條女</span>"},{"pid":"565c30a0dfc44d508e7c999f9e3ea346905dfcc2","tid":2058342,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"行樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d86a94cb4a595fc320e9e1bcc10231dfbc4e761","tid":2058342,"uid":314731,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"50973017ddf6224d41f621aaf3d9caee995b9a66","tid":2058342,"uid":8932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"因為政見同土地問題 所以 想租間工廈做studio 主要擺野 同 做野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實已經忍撚左成年 到近擺真係忍唔撚到 狂開火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" c